# jemdoc: menu{MENU}{contact.html}
= jemdoc-cvx -- contact

Bug reports, feature requests, and questions belong on the GitHub issue tracker:
[https://github.com/cvxgrp/jemdoc-cvx/issues/new https://github.com/cvxgrp/jemdoc-cvx/issues].

When filing a bug, please include the output of

~~~
{}{}
jemdoc --version
~~~

so the platform, Python version, and KaTeX availability are clear.
